---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Documents & Guides | Heavy Lifts Canada"
  description="Product information, category guidance, and supporting documents for Mammut jacks, ESCO wheel chocks, and cribbing systems."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-grid">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Product information</p>
        <h1>Documents & Guides</h1>
        <p>
          Use this section to understand the product categories, review supporting guidance, and move
          into the quote flow with better context.
        </p>
        <div class="actions">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/request-a-quote">Request a Quote</a>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/contact">Request Product Information</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <aside class="proof-panel">
        <h3>What You’ll Find Here</h3>
        <ul class="proof-list">
          <li>Category-level product information</li>
          <li>Selection guidance</li>
          <li>Document request path</li>
          <li>Quote support handoff</li>
        </ul>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Choose the Right Starting Point</h2>
    <div class="path-grid">
      <div class="path-card">
        <h3>Mammut Jacks</h3>
        <p>Best for lifting applications where capacity, starting height, and lift range drive selection.</p>
        <a class="inline-link" href="/mammut-jacks">Browse Mammut Jacks</a>
      </div>
      <div class="path-card">
        <h3>Wheel Chocks</h3>
        <p>Best for vehicle restraint needs where tire diameter, GVW, terrain, and material matter.</p>
        <a class="inline-link" href="/wheel-chocks">Browse Wheel Chocks</a>
      </div>
      <div class="path-card">
        <h3>Cribbing</h3>
        <p>Best for stabilization, support height, uneven surfaces, and structured support-system needs.</p>
        <a class="inline-link" href="/cribbing">Browse Cribbing</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section split">
    <div class="band">
      <h2>Mammut Jacks Guide</h2>
      <ul class="spec-list">
        <li>Compare capacity and height range before requesting a quote</li>
        <li>Use product detail pages to review model-level differences</li>
        <li>Send machine type, clearance, and lift-range requirements with the RFQ</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/mammut-jacks">Open Mammut Jacks</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="band">
      <h2>Wheel Chock Guide</h2>
      <ul class="spec-list">
        <li>Start with tire outside diameter and GVW range</li>
        <li>Review material and use-case differences</li>
        <li>Send terrain and operating conditions with the RFQ</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/wheel-chocks">Open Wheel Chocks</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section split">
    <div class="band">
      <h2>Cribbing & Support Guide</h2>
      <ul class="spec-list">
        <li>Decide whether you need stands, blocks, kits, or support plates</li>
        <li>Review height range and support type before requesting a quote</li>
        <li>Send load, surface condition, and support goals with the RFQ</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/cribbing">Open Cribbing</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="band band-dark">
      <h2>Need a specific document?</h2>
      <p class="lead">
        If you need a product sheet, brochure, spec reference, or help choosing the right option,
        request product information directly and include the model or category name.
      </p>
      <ul class="spec-list">
        <li>Mammut model comparisons</li>
        <li>Wheel chock sizing and selection help</li>
        <li>Cribbing and support-system guidance</li>
        <li>Accessory and quote support requests</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact">Request Product Information</a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/request-a-quote">Start a Quote Request</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
